text: ni:Sanka allaha ta'ala'e ghana yud'dhamam tamane vijaya apyo che ane"hunaina"ni lada'i vakhate pana, jyare ke tamane potana mota laskara para ghamanda hatum, parantu tene tamane kami pana phayado na pahoncadayo, visala dharati hova chatam te tamara mate tanga tha'i ga'i, pachi tame pitha batavi pacha pharya
